-- Romanian Utility Seeks Loan to Fund Waterworks in Vrancea County
-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 2013-06-26T14:53:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-06-26/romanian-utility-seeks-loan-to-fund-waterworks-in-vrancea-county.html
Cia de Utilitati Publice SA , a water
utility in eastern  Romania , is seeking a long-term loan of as
much as 40 million lei ($12 million) to upgrade water and sewage
works in Vrancea County.  Loan offers will be accepted until July 9, according to a
 procurement notice  published today on the Romanian public
auction website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Irina Savu in Bucharest at 
 isavu@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  